Package org.project3.rest_api.models

Class NutritionInfo

java.lang.Object
org.project3.rest_api.models.NutritionInfo
public class NutritionInfo extends Object
The NutritionInfo class represents the nutritional information for a menu item in the Panda Express POS system. It stores information about the menu item's allergens, calories, fat, protein, sugar, and carbohydrates.

This class includes attributes for allergens, calories, fat, protein, sugar, carbohydrates, premium status, and spicy status.

Author: Kevin Zhang

Author: Soham Nagawanshi

Author: Ryan Kha
